The '''Philippine Amateur Sepak Takraw Association''' is the national [[Sport governing body|governing body]] for [[Sepak Takraw]] in the [[Philippines]]. It  is accredited by the [[International Sepaktakraw Federation]] which is the governing body for the sport of Sepak Takraw in the world.

